><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Total sample sales ('$sampleqty'):<u></u><u></u></b></p></td><td style="padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt"><p class="MsoNormal" align="right" style="text-align:right">'$sample'<u></u><u></u></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt"><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Total sales ('$sampleqty+$allqty;'):<u></u><u></u></b></p></td><td style="padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt"><p class="MsoNormal" align="right" style="text-align:right">'$sample+$total;'<u></u><u></u></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>';
